title: shares smooching snap with Kanye West
text:
Kim Kardashian and Kanye West often look stone faced when stepping out on the town.
But on Tuesday, the 32-year-old reality star showed a different side to her relationship with her 39-year-old rapper turned fashion designer husband.
In a sweet Instagram post, the beauty was seen kissing the father of her two children. In her caption Quote: : 'Happy Valentine's Day.'

Helping her man: Here the 36-year-old is seen with a bodyguard in NYC as she supports the rapper before her presents Yeezy 5 on Wednesday
The Keeping Up With The Kardashians star - who is in NYC for Kanye's Yeezy 5 show on Wednesday - is just one of many celebrities who went to social media to spread the love.

'My littlest valentine and my Numero Uno...happy Valentine's Day!' the 39-year-old University Of Michigan graduate captioned the photo.
